    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这种工作流很常见。我需要确认几个细节：主分支叫master还是main？还有，feature分支的显示顺序要排在master前面还是后面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "master",
        "mainBranchName",
        "order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "主分支用master，这是老项目的命名。feature分支的order设为1，让它显示在master上方，视觉上更清楚。另外commit标签要显示出来，分支也要显示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "master",
        "feature",
        "order: 1",
        "showBranches",
        "showCommitLabel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先初始化配置，设置logLevel为debug方便调试，然后画出master上的第一个提交标记为V1.0。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "init",
        "debug",
        "V1.0",
